      <Value><![CDATA[<p>2022 marked an important year for the Queen Margaret Business School as it saw its inaugural cohort of students on the BA (Hons) Business Management (Graduate Apprenticeship) programme tread the boards of the Usher Hall to receive their degrees – the culmination of four years of both full-time work and education.</p>]]></Value>
